==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rad
<hw>Rad</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>r</ets>adiation <ets>a</ets>bsorbed <ets>d</ets>ose.]</ety>
<def>A unit of measurement of the amount of ionizing radiation absorbed
by an object, equal to an energy of 100 ergs per gram of irradiated
material (equal to 0.01 gray).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rad</ent>⟦br⟧

